114
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:06,878
I didn't mean it.

115
00:06:06,879 --> 00:06:07,560
Or...

116
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,480
How about I make it up to you?

117
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:10,878
Make it up for me?

118
00:06:10,879 --> 00:06:11,438
Yes.

119
00:06:11,439 --> 00:06:12,360
How?

120
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,680
What a pauper.

121
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,518
Why are you scolding me?

122
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:17,560
Why wouldn't I?

123
00:06:17,839 --> 00:06:19,160
I'll even hit you.

124
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,839
Who are you?

125
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,199
How dare you interfere in my affairs?

126
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,439
Do you know who my father...

127
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,759
You're oppressing others.

128
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:29,199
People like you

129
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,639
