130
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,240
Slap...

131
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:35,720
Slap?

132
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:38,040
Forget it.

133
00:06:38,358 --> 00:06:40,358
I'm at fault in this matter as well.

134
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,239
I'm willing to pay

135
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,079
