136
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:44,639
Who cares?

137
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:45,959
It's decided.

138
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:48,679
My name is Liu Mei.

139
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:49,479
What's your name?

140
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,279
My name is Long Mengli.

141
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:51,839
I'm applying for the position
of fashion designer.

142
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,040
Long Mengli.

143
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,160
Just wait and see.

144
00:06:56,399 --> 00:06:57,040
Ms. Lin.

145
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,160
What happened?

146
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,360
